{"tid":1992362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「尋歡」後失1200元 男子無懼疫情：我有咁嘅需要","createTime":"2020-04-28T06:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T08:19:16.000Z","uid":244460,"like":111,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"6d66dd4048ecf0abbb84e807302ed23d77f646d0","tid":1992362,"uid":244460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T06:09:33.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】一名64歲姓劉男子，凌晨到油麻地上海街附近「尋歡」，與一名非裔女子到某大廈單位度「春宵」，並同意支付200元肉金，至凌晨一時許，男事主發現銀包內兩張500元紙幣及兩張100元紙幣不翼而飛，合共損失1200元，懷疑被偷竊，報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n劉先生表示，當時衣服放在大門旁邊椅子，過程中女子未曾離開。劉先生坦言是首次光顧，又指自己三度離婚，「我無對我老婆唔住，離咗婚，我有咁嘅需要，我畀錢，正常交易。」<br />\n<br />\n近月新冠肺炎疫情持續，人人自危，劉先生仍表示不擔心，「有需要你就要咁做，唔係我都唔會咁樣走嚟呢度，係咪先，仲要搵個叉妹。係我搵佢，唔好話佢兜塔我，企晒喺街度嘛。」<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1757193/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%84%A1%E6%87%BC%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-%E5%B0%8B%E6%AD%A1-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%A4%B11200%E5%85%83-%E6%88%91%E6%9C%89%E5%92%81%E5%98%85%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1757193%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2587%25BC%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585-%25E5%25B0%258B%25E6%25AD%25A1-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A4%25B11200%25E5%2585%2583-%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2592%2581%25E5%2598%2585%25E9%259C%2580%25E8%25A6%2581&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPvrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=c3e80455\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1757193%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2587%25BC%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585-%25E5%25B0%258B%25E6%25AD%25A1-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A4%25B11200%25E5%2585%2583-%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2592%2581%25E5%2598%2585%25E9%259C%2580%25E8%25A6%2581&h=f9807ea2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1757193/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%